      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please, help",
      "zh": "請幫忙",
      "ja": "お願い、助けて",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, something...",
      "zh": "是的，某些事...",
      "ja": "はい、何か...",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cute, he's... I'm gonna keep you",
      "zh": "可愛，他是...我要留下你",
      "ja": "かわいい、彼は...君を守るよ",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I recommend we remove all magic",
