      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Will be your enemy",
      "zh": "都會成為你的敵人",
      "ja": "あなたの敵になるだろう",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No",
      "zh": "不",
      "ja": "いいえ",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want to build a snowman?",
      "zh": "你想堆雪人嗎？",
      "ja": "雪だるまを作りたい？",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It doesn't have to be a snowman",
      "zh": "不一定要是雪人",
      "ja": "雪だるまでなくてもいいよ",
