      "ja": "おお",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello",
      "zh": "你好",
      "ja": "こんにちは",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But like you, it's just me",
      "zh": "但像你一樣，只有我",
      "ja": "でも君みたいに、ただの私だ",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no",
