    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Duke of Weaselton",
      "zh": "韋塞爾頓公爵",
      "ja": "ウェッセルトン公爵",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, what?",
      "zh": "喔，什麼？",
      "ja": "ああ、何？",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You look at you",
      "zh": "你看看你自己",
      "ja": "君を見てごらん",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I don't think",
      "zh": "喔，我不認為",
      "ja": "ああ、そうは思わない",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you swoon let me know",
      "zh": "如果你昏倒了告訴我",
      "ja": "もし気絶したら教えて",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll catch it",
      "zh": "我會接住你",
      "ja": "受け止めるよ",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, he was sprightly",
      "zh": "嗯，他很活潑",
      "ja": "彼は元気だった",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Especially for a man in heels",
      "zh": "尤其是穿高跟鞋的男人",
      "ja": "特にヒールを履いた男にしては",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Glad I caught you",
      "zh": "很高興我抓住你了",
      "ja": "捕まえられてよかった",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hons",
      "zh": "漢斯",
      "ja": "ハンス",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's this?",
      "zh": "這是什麼？",
      "ja": "これは何？",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was born with it",
      "zh": "我天生就有的",
      "ja": "生まれつきだ",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One day she just shut me out",
      "zh": "有一天她突然把我拒之門外",
      "ja": "ある日彼女は私を締め出した",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I never knew why",
      "zh": "我從不知道為什麼",
      "ja": "なぜかは知らなかった",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But with you",
      "zh": "但和你在一起",
      "ja": "でも君となら",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But with you",
      "zh": "但和你在一起",
      "ja": "でも君となら",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I thought my eyes are seen",
      "zh": "我以為我的眼睛被看見了",
      "ja": "目が見られていると思った",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And all",
      "zh": "以及一切",
      "ja": "そしてすべて",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm not a single thing",
      "zh": "我不是一無是處",
      "ja": "私は何もないわけじゃない",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can see something even crazier",
      "zh": "我能看到更瘋狂的東西",
      "ja": "もっとクレイジーなものが見える",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes",
      "zh": "是的",
      "ja": "はい",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Of our marriage",
      "zh": "關於我們的婚姻",
      "ja": "私たちの結婚について",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How rich you are",
      "zh": "你多麼富有",
      "ja": "君はどれほど裕福か",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No one is getting married",
      "zh": "沒有人會結婚",
      "ja": "誰も結婚しない",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait, what?",
      "zh": "等等，什麼？",
      "ja": "ちょっと、何？",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "May I talk to you please",
      "zh": "我可以跟你談談嗎？",
      "ja": "お話ししてもいいですか？",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, you may not",
      "zh": "不，你不行",
      "ja": "いいえ、ダメです",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I think you should go",
      "zh": "我覺得你應該走了",
      "ja": "行ったほうがいいと思う",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The party is over",
      "zh": "派對結束了",
      "ja": "パーティーは終わった",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Close the gates",
      "zh": "關上大門",
      "ja": "門を閉めろ",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you so afraid?",
      "zh": "你這麼害怕嗎？",
      "ja": "そんなに怖いのか？",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I said, you know",
      "zh": "我說，你知道",
      "ja": "言っただろう",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I said, you can't",
      "zh": "我說，你不能",
      "ja": "言っただろう、できないと",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I said, you can't",
      "zh": "我說，你不能",
      "ja": "言っただろう、できないと",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I said, you can't",
      "zh": "我說，你不能",
      "ja": "言っただろう、できないと",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop her",
      "zh": "阻止她",
      "ja": "彼女を止めろ",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please just stay away from me",
      "zh": "請離我遠一點",
      "ja": "どうか私から離れて",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay away",
      "zh": "遠離",
      "ja": "離れて",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait, please",
      "zh": "等等，拜託",
      "ja": "待って、お願い",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My sister's not a monster",
      "zh": "我妹妹不是怪物",
      "ja": "私の妹は怪物じゃない",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She nearly killed me",
      "zh": "她差點殺了我",
      "ja": "彼女は私を殺しかけた",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
