      "time": "00:09:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry about me",
      "zh": "別擔心我",
      "ja": "私のことは心配しないで",
      "time": "00:09:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's in here",
      "zh": "他在這裡",
      "ja": "彼はここにいる",
      "time": "00:09:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Prince Hans",
      "zh": "漢斯王子",
      "ja": "ハンス王子",
      "time": "00:09:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna",
      "zh": "安娜",
      "ja": "アナ",
      "time": "00:09:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're so cold",
      "zh": "你真冷",
      "ja": "君はとても冷たい",
      "time": "00:09:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She froze my heart",
      "zh": "她凍結了我的心",
      "ja": "彼女は私の心を凍らせた",
      "time": "00:09:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And only an active true love can save me",
      "zh": "只有真正的愛能救我",
      "ja": "本当の愛だけが私を救える",
      "time": "00:09:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You said you did",
      "zh": "你說你做到了",
      "ja": "君はそう言った",
      "time": "00:09:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Accident, Pralza",
      "zh": "意外，普拉爾扎",
      "ja": "事故だ、プラルザ",
